853
00:52:07,640 --> 00:52:10,230
World domination would be easier. 

854
00:52:10,230 --> 00:52:14,140
Dating is a game where the one who loves more loses. 

855
00:52:14,140 --> 00:52:15,630
I think so, too. 

856
00:52:16,120 --> 00:52:19,510
To beat the rival,
you must get to the next stage. 

857
00:52:19,510 --> 00:52:20,950
Physical contact. 

858
00:52:20,950 --> 00:52:22,100
Physical contact? 

859
00:52:22,100 --> 00:52:22,790
Kissing. 

