862
00:52:26,890 --> 00:52:28,210
Oh, right. It's not me. 

863
00:52:28,580 --> 00:52:31,060
Tell my friend to kiss him first? 

864
00:52:31,060 --> 00:52:34,180
No, men don't like forward women. 

865
00:52:34,180 --> 00:52:37,200
You must make him want to kiss you. 

866
00:52:37,200 --> 00:52:38,470
How? 

