00:53:42,370 --> 00:53:43,920
It's exciting. 

871
00:53:43,920 --> 00:53:46,390
It feels like I'm losing weight. 

872
00:53:49,720 --> 00:53:52,330
I like your perfume. 

873
00:53:54,180 --> 00:53:55,830
It's my shampoo. 

874
00:54:24,900 --> 00:54:26,350
She has a date. 

875
00:54:26,350 --> 00:54:28,150
It must be going well with that man from the blind date. 

876
00:54:41,870 --> 00:54:43,190
Ugh! 

877
00:54:43,800 --> 00:54:44,980
Ouch! Ouch... 

878
00:54:44,980 --> 00:54:46,440
Stop doing stuff like that. 

879
00:54:46,440 --> 00:54:48,170
Hey! Where were you? 

880
00:54:48,170 --> 00:54:49,770
My bat's been crying out your name! 

881
00:54:49,770 --> 00:54:51,770
As if I'm not mad enough already. 

882
00:54:55,360 --> 00:54:57,120
What are you doing this weekend? 

883
00:54:57,580 --> 00:54:59,820
I have a business trip to China. 

884
00:54:59,820 --> 00:55:01,460
Is it a long trip? 

885
00:55:01,460 --> 00:55:02,640
About 3 days? 

886
00:55:03,080 --> 00:55:04,750
You want a present, don't you? 

887
00:55:05,490 --> 00:55:06,750
Wrong. 

888
00:55:07,510 --> 00:55:11,550
But I won't refuse it if you bring me one. 

889
00:55:11,550 --> 00:55:12,830
Can I tell you what I want? 

890
00:55:12,830 --> 00:55:13,570
Sure. 

891
00:55:20,280 --> 00:55:21,750
Huh? Me? 

892
00:55:22,920 --> 00:55:23,710
Yes. 

893
00:55:24,110 --> 00:55:26,210
Come back safely. 

894
00:55:26,210 --> 00:55:28,210
That'll be the best present. 

895
00:55:30,240 --> 00:55:32,870
Let's hurry up.
I have a curfew. 

896
00:55:32,870 --> 00:55:34,890
You have a curfew?
How old are you? 

897
00:55:34,890 --> 00:55:38,900
My mom is really strict because she had to raise me on her own. 

898
00:55:38,900 --> 00:55:43,380
She said a woman must be very careful. 

899
00:55:43,380 --> 00:55:46,950
It used to be 9 but now its 10 pm. 

900
00:55:46,950 --> 00:55:49,890
And on special occasions it's midnight. 

901
00:55:50,720 --> 00:55:52,690
And tonight's a special occasion? 

902
00:55:53,080 --> 00:55:54,130
Yes. 

903
00:55:58,080 --> 00:56:01,600
Ugh! That hit the spot. 

904
00:56:01,880 --> 00:56:04,280
Trying to act demure was hard, mom. 

905
00:56:04,930 --> 00:56:06,740
Did he fall for you? 

906
00:56:06,740 --> 00:56:09,910
I told you.
Nobody can escape from me. 

907
00:56:10,480 --> 00:56:11,900
He'll fall for me hard. 

908
00:56:11,900 --> 00:56:15,270
Oh, I feel bad for him. 

909
00:56:15,680 --> 00:56:17,950
Yeongdal, how do you do it? 

910
00:56:17,950 --> 00:56:19,780
Teach me how you do it. 

911
00:56:19,780 --> 00:56:21,140
But what would you do with that? 

912
00:56:21,550 --> 00:56:25,040
Everything you learn will come in handy someday, except for how to rob a house. 

913
00:56:25,940 --> 00:56:28,050
I'm just saying. 

914
00:56:28,050 --> 00:56:29,320
Listen carefully. 

915
00:56:29,320 --> 00:56:31,470
You must use different techniques. 

916
00:56:31,470 --> 00:56:33,720
Men in their 20s fall for your looks. 

917
00:56:33,720 --> 00:56:36,090
Men in their 30s fall for your money. 

918
00:56:36,760 --> 00:56:38,800
Men look at women's money? 

919
00:56:39,550 --> 00:56:42,080
Then again, it's a difficult time. 

920
00:56:42,080 --> 00:56:44,300
Both women and men are money crazy. 

921
00:56:45,000 --> 00:56:47,460
With him, I can't be money crazy. 

922
00:56:48,140 --> 00:56:50,770
I must pretend to be humble and naive. 

923
00:56:51,450 --> 00:56:54,740
It's my dream to become a good wife. 

924
00:56:54,740 --> 00:56:56,080
And that works? 

925
00:56:57,080 --> 00:57:02,240
Oh, well, a rich man wouldn't need to make his wife work. 

926
00:57:02,240 --> 00:57:05,570
I'm answering my own question. 

927
00:57:08,050 --> 00:57:10,910
Oh, I can't drink. 

928
00:57:10,910 --> 00:57:12,720
It's my first time. 

929
00:57:12,720 --> 00:57:14,890
I have a curfew, so I must go home. 

930
00:57:14,890 --> 00:57:17,020
My mom is very strict. 

931
00:57:17,020 --> 00:57:19,560
This is what I do. 

932
00:57:19,560 --> 00:57:24,660
You got awful grades at school,
but you're really good at things like this. 

933
00:57:24,660 --> 00:57:27,570
It's because you took after me. 

934
00:57:29,700 --> 00:57:31,310
Oh, he's going on a business trip. 

935
00:57:31,820 --> 00:57:33,330
Did you ask him to bring a present? 

936
00:57:33,900 --> 00:57:36,670
That's what the dumb girls do. 

937
00:57:36,670 --> 00:57:37,990
I'm different. 

938
00:57:39,220 --> 00:57:41,100
Have a safe trip. 

939
00:57:41,100 --> 00:57:43,160
That'll be the best present. 

940
00:57:43,470 --> 00:57:46,760
Oh, you're crafty. 

941
00:57:46,760 --> 00:57:51,090
Dumb girls get greedy about little things and end up losing what's important. 

942
00:57:51,090 --> 00:57:54,100
You have to look ahead.
Way ahead. 

943
00:57:54,100 --> 00:57:56,540
Way into the future so I can milk him. 

944
00:57:56,540 --> 00:58:00,130
Oh, you're such a smart girl! 

945
00:58:00,130 --> 00:58:01,990
Why do you think I dated all those men? 

946
00:58:01,990 --> 00:58:04,640
I learned how to pick the best man. 

947
00:58:04,640 --> 00:58:06,290
Experience is knowledge. 

948
00:58:06,290 --> 00:58:07,650
Just wait, mom. 

949
00:58:07,650 --> 00:58:11,480
He'll buy me a luxury brand handbag and propose to me in a month. 

950
00:58:11,690 --> 00:58:13,890
Please make that happen. 

951
00:58:15,900 --> 00:58:18,380
Don't be sad about not moving with Sedal. 

952
00:58:18,380 --> 00:58:23,090
I'll make sure we live in a great big house. 

953
00:58:23,780 --> 00:58:26,060
Just hearing that makes me happy. 

954
00:58:26,060 --> 00:58:28,180
Find a good husband. 

955
00:58:28,180 --> 00:58:30,840
I'm going to crush Anggeum. 

956
00:58:30,840 --> 00:58:33,770
Though she's halfway there already. 

957
00:58:34,150 --> 00:58:35,770
Oh... 

958
00:58:39,390 --> 00:58:41,580
Mom, can't we eat first? 

959
00:58:42,010 --> 00:58:43,420
Hold on. 

960
00:58:43,420 --> 00:58:46,420
Grandmother, great grandmother and aunt are coming. 

961
00:58:46,700 --> 00:58:49,190
Oh... This is torture. 

962
00:59:34,080 --> 00:59:36,200
Slow down.
You'll get a stomachache. 

963
00:59:36,200 --> 00:59:37,970
Mom, it's good even when it's soggy. 

964
00:59:37,970 --> 00:59:39,480
Mom, you eat too. 

965
00:59:42,590 --> 00:59:45,870
I'll eat later with your grandmother. 

966
00:59:46,100 --> 00:59:48,710
Mom, can I have just one piece of pork? 

967
00:59:49,210 --> 00:59:51,580
You shouldn't touch it before the adults eat. 

968
00:59:51,580 --> 00:59:52,720
Just one! 

969
00:59:52,720 --> 00:59:55,780
We should be grateful about the noodles. 

970
01:00:02,740 --> 01:00:05,200
This is nuts. 

971
01:00:05,200 --> 01:00:09,400
The only time I ate out was when I had black bean noodles on my painful anniversary. 

972
01:00:10,490 --> 01:00:11,890
Painful anniversary? 

973
01:00:12,950 --> 01:00:13,890
Yes. 

974
01:00:13,890 --> 01:00:17,600
Painful days come right after your wedding. 

975
01:00:17,600 --> 01:00:19,550
Only those who've done it can understand. 

976
01:00:20,370 --> 01:00:23,870
My wife would go nuts if she came here. 

977
01:00:24,890 --> 01:00:29,420
This is like straight out of a movie. 

978
01:00:29,420 --> 01:00:31,520
I'm the male star and you are... 

979
01:00:31,520 --> 01:00:32,480
Enough. 

980
01:00:32,970 --> 01:00:34,720
- Let's drink.
- Okay. 

