Sintong!  

982
01:01:13,210 --> 01:01:14,380
Bangtong! 

983
01:01:16,920 --> 01:01:19,340
Sintong, wake up. Wake up. 

984
01:01:19,340 --> 01:01:21,210
Bangtong, have some sweet and sour pork. 

985
01:01:21,210 --> 01:01:22,960
Get up and eat sweet and sour pork. 

986
01:01:35,390 --> 01:01:39,010
Eat. You said you wanted it. Eat. 

987
01:01:39,010 --> 01:01:40,470
It doesn't taste good. 

988
01:01:40,470 --> 01:01:42,690
Why didn't you give it to us before? 

989
01:01:43,150 --> 01:01:44,840
Mom, I'm full. 

990
01:01:45,850 --> 01:01:47,290
I'm sleepy. 

991
01:01:51,480 --> 01:01:52,460
Go to bed. 

992
01:01:53,430 --> 01:01:55,300
Wow... 

993
01:02:02,880 --> 01:02:05,740
Dad, I told you to leave me alone. 

994
01:02:05,740 --> 01:02:11,060
What am I supposed to do with a man who hasn't called me since I came back? 

995
01:02:12,910 --> 01:02:14,400
It's over between us! 

996
01:02:44,570 --> 01:03:09,800
Subtitles by KBS World 

997
01:03:10,250 --> 01:03:12,810
What are you doing here?
To say goodbye? 

998
01:03:12,810 --> 01:03:15,450
